  "text": "14 In this study, survival outcomes were similar to our findings favoring the local treatment cohort. Another retrospective study of 408 patients with nasopharyngeal cancer demonstrated a survival benefit with the up-front use of radiotherapy with systemic therapy, [CITATION_1] further supporting our findings.",
